com.esri.mo2.map.ext
Interface ExtractExtension

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable, LayerExtension
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseExtractExtension
public interface ExtractExtension
extends LayerExtension

Implements an Extract LayerExtension, that is used for layers involved in data downloading activities from an ArcIMS ExtractService.

public boolean getClip()
